<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 248, 248); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify; line-height: 35px; font-size: 14px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 35px;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">会议开始，学生党支部书记陈莹和学生党员们一起阅读了习主席的新年贺词和《求是》杂志上发表的习主席的重要讲话内容，学习了其中的精神。各位学生党员同志仔细聆听陈书记的讲解并认真做笔记。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmELI05DQcGVmdIBhibaZEib6X1bxRZWnh6MFMb3cfNYSH8hv3KZibs7lfaGfog4VDSuDHDYNibCiaUHBDTw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="308" height="202" style="width: 308px; height: 202px;"/></span></p></section></section></section></section><p></p><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="118215" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 248, 248); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 20px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; transform-style: preserve-3d;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center; transform: translateZ(10px);"></section></section></section></section></section><p></p><p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 248, 248); font-size: 24px;">之后，经济管理学院党总支书记蔡平发表讲话。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 248, 248); font-size: 24px;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2n18Qa8gmELI05DQcGVmdIBhibaZEib6X1TRv5PESX1YqcficeQ6U2uEU6cukgpUFHibkzqHmvPMdW8g8fGFfb9ZRg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="319" height="247" style="width: 319px; height: 247px;"/></span></p>